org.dspace.content.dao

Interface BitstreamFormatDAO

  • All Superinterfaces:
    GenericDAO<BitstreamFormat>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BitstreamFormatDAOImpl

    public interface BitstreamFormatDAO
extends GenericDAO<BitstreamFormat>
    Database Access Object interface class for the BitstreamFormat object. The implementation of this class is responsible for all database calls for the BitstreamFormat object and is autowired by spring This class should only be accessed from a single service and should never be exposed outside of the API
    Author:
    kevinvandevelde at atmire.com
